org.funcito.mode

  • Packages that use org.funcito.mode 
    Package Description
    org.funcito
    Funcito is a method-wrapping library for Java, to assist in using several Java functional programming frameworks.
    org.funcito.collectionsgeneric
    Funcito public interface into the collections-generic API.
    org.funcito.functionaljava
    Funcito public interface into the Functional Java API.
    org.funcito.functorfactory  
    org.funcito.guava
    Funcito public interface into the Gooogle Guava API.
    org.funcito.jedi
    Funcito public interface into the Jedi API.
    org.funcito.mode
    Mode and TypedMode interfaces and core implementations.
    org.funcito.play
    Funcito public interface into the Play! Framework 2 API.
    org.funcito.rxjava
    Funcito public interface into the Netflix RxJava API.
  • Classes in org.funcito.mode used by org.funcito 
    Class and Description
    Mode
    The execution of every functor object created by a Funcito factory method is guided by an instance of either a standard Mode (this interface) or its cousin TypedMode.
    TypedMode
    The execution of every functor object created by a Funcito factory method is guided by an instance of either a standard Mode or its cousin, TypedMode (this interface).
